OUT OF 4 EMPLOYEES ,2 WERE RECIVED BONUS


THEY NEED FIND THE EMPLOYEE WHOSE BONUS LESS THAN 1000


MANAGMENT HAVE SOME PAIN POINT


THEY WANT INCREASE THEIR REVENUE

WITH AVAILABLE DATA HOW CAN THEY DO THAT

THERE IS ONE SIGNAL IF EMPLOYEE RECIVED BONUS LESS THAN 1000 INDICATES THEY ARE 
LESS EFFICIENT 


THEY NEED TO IDENTIFY THE EMPLOYEE,TRAIN THEM TO REACH MORE EFFICIENT

AS A RESULT THEY WILL INCREASE THEIR PROFIT MARGIN.


